<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-12">
    <h1>今、話題の趣味は…</h1>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-10 col-md-offset-1">
    <p class="text-center" style="font-size: 100px"><%= @showHobby.name %></p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-1 col-md-offset-10" style="font-size: 20px;">
    <%= link_to 'more...', hobbies_path %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-12" style="font-size: 24px;">
    <p>あなたの一押しの趣味を教えてください</p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <%= form_for @hobby,:url => {:action => :create} do |f| %>
  <div class="col-sm-11">
    <%= f.text_field :name , class:'form-control' %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-1">
    <%= f.submit '投稿', class:'btn btn-default' %>
  </div>
  <% end %>
</div>
